[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1442[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Running the demo against the in-memory mocks produces output like this. Numbers vary because of the synthetic-data noise but the segmentation, the model selection, and the prediction-interval logic are deterministic given the seed.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
